# These showcase images are published verbatim to the PUBLIC Rei-Demo repo by
# .github/workflows/publish-showcase.yml (which checks out with lfs:false).
# The repo-root .gitattributes forces *.png/*.jpg/*.gif into Git LFS — that would
# publish LFS POINTER files (broken images) and burn the public repo's tiny LFS
# bandwidth quota. Override it here so these assets are stored as plain git blobs.
# (See docs/specs/demo-repo-publishing.md §4 rule 3.)
*.png  !filter !diff !merge -text
*.jpg  !filter !diff !merge -text
*.jpeg !filter !diff !merge -text
*.gif  !filter !diff !merge -text
